Requirements:
===================

- java

- ant 

- libevent

    $ wget http://monkey.org/~provos/libevent-2.0.12-stable.tar.gz
    $ tar xfvz libevent-2.0.12-stable.tar.gz
    $ cd libevent-2.0.12-stable
    $ ./configure --prefix=/usr/local
    $ make
    $ sudo make install

- thrift

    $ wget http://apache.petsads.us//thrift/0.6.1/thrift-0.6.1.tar.gz
    $ tar xfvz thrift-0.6.1.tar.gz
    $ cd thrift-0.6.1
    $ ./configure --prefix=/usr/local
    $ make
    $ sudo make install
